snippet.title: Undertale Together - UnderEvent 2022 Trailer
snippet.description:
I finally decided to make a trailer!
I am so happy that I was able to participate in "UnderEvent", a Nintendo Direct styled presentation featuring UNDERTALE fan games and other projects.
I really thank you so much for the support I recieve for this little project.
You don't know how happy it makes me.


Download: https://www.moddb.com/mods/undertale-together
Tutorial: https://youtu.be/BlPe_5AV1nI
UnderEvent 2022: https://youtu.be/TSOyg3n0GFM
Amazing cover used: https://youtu.be/IoIOerli7l8
Discord server: https://discord.gg/yhZMgHe

Undertale Together is a mod that allows you to play the entire original Undertale with two players! (3-4p WIP)
Cutscenes, fights, story, dialogues was modified to fill the experience with a friend!
